\c 18
\s Mubairo wevapristi VaRevhi
\p
\v 1 Vapristi VaRevhi, rudzi rwose rwaRevhi, havangavi nemugove kana nhaka pamwe naIsraeri\x + Num. 18.20. Num. 26.62.\x*; vachadya zvipo zvemoto zvaJehovha nenhaka yake\x + Num. 18.8,9. 1 VaKori. 9.13.\x*.
\v 2 Naizvozvo havangavi nenhaka pakati pehama dzavo; Jehovha inhaka yavo, sezvaakataura kwavari.
\p
\v 3 Zvino izvi zvichava faniro yevapristi kubva kuvanhu, kubva kune vanopa chibairo, ingava nzombe kana gwai; uye vachapa kumupristi bandauko neshaya mbiri nechasusu\x + Rev. 7.30-34.\x*.
\v 4 Zvekutanga zvezviyo zvako, zvewaini yako itsva, nezvemafuta ako, nezvekutanga zvemvere dzemakwai ako, uchapa kwaari\x + Eki. 22.29. Num. 18.12.\x*.
\v 5 Nokuti Jehovha Mwari wako wakamusarudza kubva pamarudzi ako ose, kuti amire \add pa\add*kushumira muzita raJehovha, iye nevanakomana vake mazuva ose\x + 17.12.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Zvino kana muRevhi akabva kune rimwe remasuwo ako kubva Israeri wose, kwaanogara semweni, akauya\x + Num. 35.2,3.\x* nechido chose chemoyo wake\x + 12.15.\x* kunzvimbo Jehovha yaachasarudza\x + 12.5.\x*,
\v 7 ipapo achashumira muzita raJehovha Mwari wake\x + 17.12.\x*, sehama dzake dzose VaRevhi\x + 1 Makor. 23.6. 2 Makor. 31.2.\x*, vakamirapo pamberi paJehovha\x + 17.12.\x*.
\v 8 Vachadya migove yakaenzana, kunze kwe\add zvinobva\add* pakutengeswa kwenhaka yake yemadzibaba\x + 2 Makor. 31.4. Neh. 12.44,47. 13.10.\x*.
\s Havafaniri kutevera tsika dzevahedheni
\p
\v 9 Paunosvika munyika Jehovha Mwari wako yaanokupa, usadzidza kuita zvinoenderana nezvinyangadzo zvemarudzi awo\x + Rev. 18.26-30. 12.29-31.\x*.
\v 10 Hakungawanikwi pakati pako anopinza mwanakomana wake kana mwanasikana wake nemumoto\x + Rev. 18.21.\x*, mushandisi wekushopera\x + 18.14. Num. 22.7. 23.23. Josh. 13.22; 1 Sam. 15.23; 28.8. 2 Madz. 17.17.\x*, anodudzira mashura\x + 18.14. Mik. 5.12; Isa. 2.6; Rev. 19.26.\x*, kana anoita mashiripiti\x + Rev. 19.26. Num. 24.1.\x*, kana muroyi\x + Eki. 7.11. Isa. 47.9.\x*,
\v 11 kana mutsingi wezvitsinga\x + Map. 58.5. Isa. 47.9.\x*, kana unobvunza masvikiro\x + Rev. 20.27. Rev. 19.31.\x*, kana anoita masaramusi\x + Rev. 20.27. Rev. 19.31.\x*, kana anobvunza vakafa\x + 1 Sam. 28.7.\x*.
\v 12 Nokuti wose anoita zvinhu izvi chinyangadzo kuna Jehovha; uye nekuda kwezvinyangadzo izvi Jehovha Mwari wako anovadzinga panhaka pamberi pako\x + Rev. 18.24,25. Det. 9.4.\x*.
\v 13 Uchava wakakwana kuna Jehovha Mwari wako.
\v 14 Nokuti marudzi awa auchagara nhaka, akateerera vanodudzira mashura\x + 18.14. Mik. 5.12; Isa. 2.6; Rev. 19.26.\x* nevashoperi\x + 18.14. Num. 22.7. 23.23. Josh. 13.22; 1 Sam. 15.23; 28.8. 2 Madz. 17.17.\x*; asi iwe, Jehovha Mwari wako haana kukutendera saizvozvo.
\p
\v 15 Jehovha Mwari wako achakumutsira muporofita kubva pakati pako, pahama dzako, wakafanana neni; kwaari muchateerera\x + 18.18. Joh. 1.21,25,45. Mab. 3.22. 7.37.\x*;
\v 16 zvichienderana nezvose zvawakakumbira kuna Jehovha Mwari wako paHorebhu nezuva reungano\x + 9.10.\x*, uchiti: Ndirege kunzwazve inzwi raJehovha Mwari wangu, uye ndirege kuzoonazve moto uyu mukuru, kuti ndisafa\x + Eki. 20.19.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino Jehovha wakati kwandiri: Vaita zvakanaka zvavataura\x + 5.28.\x*.
\v 18 Ndichavamutsira muporofita kubva pakati pehama dzavo wakafanana newe\x + 18.15.\x*; uye ndichaisa mashoko angu mumuromo make\x + Jer. 1.9. 5.14. Joh. 17.8.\x*; uye achataura kwavari zvose zvandinomuraira\x + Joh. 4.25. Joh. 8.28. 12.49,50.\x*.
\v 19 Zvino zvichaitika, ani nani angarega kuteerera kumashoko angu aachataura muzita rangu, ini ndicha\add zvi\add*bvunza kwaari\x + Mab. 3.23.\x*.
\v 20 Asi muporofita anozvikudza\x + 17.12.\x* achitaura shoko muzita rangu, randisina kumuraira kutaura\x + 13.5. Jer. 14.14,15. Zek. 13.3.\x*, uye anotaura muzita revamwe vamwari, muporofita uyo achafa\x + Jer. 2.8.\x*.
\v 21 Zvino kana uchiti mumoyo mako: Tichaziva sei shoko Jehovha raasina kutaura?
\v 22 Panotaura muporofita muzita raJehovha\x + Jer. 28.9; Det. 13.1-3.\x*, kana chinhu icho chikasaitika kana kuti chikasasvika, ndiro shoko Jehovha raasina kutaura; muporofita wakaritaura nekuzvikudza; usamutya\x + 18.20.\x*.